{"tid":1525274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求已經冇用","createTime":"2019-08-31T21:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T21:55:44.000Z","uid":294432,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f1812a4f081d4dcef125cbae2fce3a94a0d399d3","tid":1525274,"uid":294432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:23:24.000Z","msg":"[P牌第一次投稿，請諒解]<br />\n<br />\n抗爭兩個幾月，垃圾政府完全冇回應過香港人既五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n零反省，反而更不擇手段加強武力鎮壓示威者。<br />\n佢地治根不治本，繼續落去只會有更多人受傷同手足被補。<br />\n<br />\n呢個政府同警隊根本就係廢！<br />\n<br />\n我地係咪應該要更改訴求，直接要 重組政府，解散警隊呢？<br />\n<br />\n純粹意見，希望大家可以參考同討論。"},{"pid":"049e1f3575f920f07620963d3fb6057807b7e14d","tid":1525274,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:26:40.000Z","msg":"中共倒台"},{"pid":"732d22b62b4fc89ef56adda87258b31a6a3787f6","tid":1525274,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:27:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【國際路線】全世界印同舉依款標語</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifcqnMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FifcqnMz.png&h=19bda72c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/taez0yf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftaez0yf.png&h=868ecca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttTpDjV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttTpDjV.png&h=ada7f3ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2a63581a7463d9793f46def34cf8c71d8261ea8","tid":1525274,"uid":15155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:29:28.000Z","msg":"就算聽日政府食晒五大訴求都已經找唔到數<br />\n而你講的重組政府<br />\n即係革命"},{"pid":"c70deabe5e25bd4ebe6ecce0a0f85d05b88f1595","tid":1525274,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:32:26.000Z","msg":"柒婆講到明唔接受啦"},{"pid":"4b05c8636a395db6a7228910392e16706b57b650","tid":1525274,"uid":174174,"l